scenes.description: Moona Hoshinova performing 'Who's Toxic? It's You!' on stage with robotic backup dancers.
MC section where Moona talks to the audience in Indonesian and English, expressing excitement about her 3D live and introducing her backup dancers, the 'Monavitas'.
Moona performs a quick costume change on stage into her birthday merchandise T-shirt and introduces the next song.
Moona performing the song 'DEJAVU' with a live band concept.
